Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.52,0:00:02.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Do you...}Ngươi...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.10,0:00:06.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{really think you can just take a gold coin?}thực sự nghĩ có thể cướp được xu vàng sao?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.40,0:00:12.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{From me?\NThe magma master of Orca dorm...}Từ ta? Bậc thầy dùng magma của nhà Orca...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.57,0:00:15.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Rhodes Eamus!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.37,0:00:25.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{I had heard you were\Nsurprisingly aggressive for an Orca...}Ta nghe đồn người rất mạnh và hung hãn...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.42,0:00:30.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{But you were nothing more, it seems.}Nhưng cũng chẳng mạnh lắm nhỉ.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.91,0:02:23.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Magically talented, and high self-esteem...}Tài năng ma lực, lòng tự tôn cao ngất...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.49,0:02:29.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Lang's elite, Magia Lupus,\Nis filled with students of that nature.}Những kẻ mạnh nhất của nhà Lang, Magia Lupus, \Ntoàn những kẻ mang bản chất đó.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.04,0:02:33.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Its higher ranks are clearly\Nthe top students in this school.}Chúng rõ ràng là những kẻ đứng\N ở vị trí cao nhất trong trường.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.67,0:02:38.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{I'd rather not play defense\Nagainst those with actual skills...}Tao không thích chơi phòng thủ trước chúng...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.05,0:02:43.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{But this school hides\Nthe dorms' locations from each other.}Nhưng trường học này giấu vị trí các nhà.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.97,0:02:47.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{This is to encourage\Ninter-dorm competition.}Nhằm khuyến khích cạnh tranh công bằng.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.18,0:02:49.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{That's why...}Đó là lý do...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.89,0:02:53.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{we're going to figure out where\Nthey are, so we can take their coins.}chúng ta sẽ tìm ra chỗ của chúng và cướp hết xu vàng.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.61,0:02:58.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{'Kay.}Đi.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.45,0:03:02.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Were you really listening?}Mày có nghe không thế?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.03,0:03:07.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Lastly, it's been a month\Nsince you were admitted.}Đã 1 tháng từ khi mày vào trường.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.20,0:03:10.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Here's your dorm robe. Put it on.}Đây là áo khoác của mày. Mặc đi.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.66,0:03:11.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{'Kay.}Rồi.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.75,0:03:18.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{You're joking around, right?}Mày giỡn mặt à?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.67,0:03:21.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Whoa, the logo.}Ồ, logo luôn.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.68,0:03:24.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{That's not a logo. That's Adler's mark.}Không phải logo. Biểu tượng của nhà Adler.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.64,0:03:28.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{And by the way, logos are letters\Nthat have been transformed into a design.}Cơ mà logo là chữ đã được chuyển đổi bằng thiết kế.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.89,0:03:29.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{'Kay.}Hiểu.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.93,0:03:34.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{I hope this makes you more conscious\Nof the fact that you belong to a dorm.}Tao hi vọng mày ý thức được \Nbản thân mình thuộc về nhà nào.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.44,0:03:35.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{But first...}Nhưng đầu tiên...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.73,0:03:37.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Mash!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.15,0:03:39.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Big trouble! Tom is...}Lớn chuyện rồi! Anh Tom...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.99,0:03:43.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{- Can you hold on? My cream puffs...\N- But Tom...}Khoan đã, bánh su kem của tớ--\N Anh Tom đã...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.78,0:03:45.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{No, my cream puffs...}Không, bánh su kem...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.32,0:03:47.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Tom!}Anh Tom!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.95,0:03:49.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{They went to the infirmary.}{\i0}Họ đến phòng y tế.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.54,0:03:55.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Hey, guys...\NHow are you all... bambooing?}Mấy đứa à... Có khoẻ như cây tre không?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.58,0:03:58.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Or are you more like bamboo-it?}Hay giống như bamboo?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.42,0:04:00.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Captain's character identity...}Bản chất của anh ấy...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.67,0:04:03.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{What happened? You look so drained.}Chuyện gì đã xảy ra? Bộ dạng tơi tả đó...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.26,0:04:08.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{That's the thing. I don't really remember.}Thực ra anh cũng chẳng nhớ.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.60,0:04:10.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{When I woke up, I was here.}Khi tỉnh dậy đã thấy nằm đây.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.98,0:04:15.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Usually I live my life at full throttle\Nso I fall asleep and bam, it's morning.}Bình thường anh sống hết mình \Nvà ngủ một mạch tới sáng.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.19,0:04:17.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Anh không bao giờ mơ.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.19,0:04:20.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{But the night I collapsed...}Nhưng trước ngày bị bất tỉnh...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.65,0:04:26.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{I dreamt that I was trapped\Nand stuffed in some dark box.}Anh mơ thấy mình bị nhốt trong một cái hộp.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.45,0:04:31.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{I was fully conscious but couldn't speak.}Không thể nói thành tiếng nhưng ý thức vẫn còn.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.20,0:04:34.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{I was in that state for hours.}Anh đã ở đó vài tiếng.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.08,0:04:38.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{It was such a nightmare.}Nó là cơn ác mộng.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.96,0:04:40.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Captain is so shook up.}Đội trưởng trông tiều tuỵ quá...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.46,0:04:43.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{I need to eat a cream puff.}Em phải ăn bánh su kem thôi.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.63,0:04:45.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Mash, please keep it down.}Mash, đừng bày trò nữa.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.14,0:04:49.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Are you okay physically?}Anh ổn chứ?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.76,0:04:52.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Yeah. I just feel slightly woozy.}Anh cảm thấy cơ thể nhẹ quá.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.23,0:04:54.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Also...}Với cả...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.73,0:04:57.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{I'm temporarily unable to use magic.}Anh không thể sử dụng ma thuật.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.27,0:05:01.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{I hardly feel magical energy within me.}Rất khó để cảm nhận năng lượng trong người.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.82,0:05:04.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{It's like someone sucked it out of me...}Cứ như vòi nước bị tắc vậy.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.49,0:05:08.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{I see. But in any case...}Ra là vậy. Cơ mà...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.33,0:05:11.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Why are there so many here?}Số lượng này là sao?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.75,0:05:18.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Yeah. They all seem to have lost\Ntheir magic temporarily, too.}Ờ, có vẻ họ cũng giống như anh.\N Không thể dùng ma thuật.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.79,0:05:23.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Right when our headmaster\Ngot called out to the Bureau of Magic...}Ngay lúc Hiệu trưởng bị gọi về Cục Ma thuật...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.80,0:05:27.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Um, Mash. Take this.}Mash, cầm lấy.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.35,0:05:31.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{HONK}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.81,0:05:33.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{What's this?}Đéo gì đây?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.06,0:05:36.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{That's Creamy.\NShe's a good luck charm I made.}Creamy. Bùa hộ mệnh tớ làm cho cậu đó.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.10,0:05:40.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{I've been feeling a little anxious lately.}Gần đây tớ có cảm giác bất an.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.02,0:05:42.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{What's with the ribbon?}Cái nơ này là sao?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.07,0:05:44.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{You're so tactless!}Cậu thiếu tế nhị quá đó!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.95,0:05:51.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{In any case,\Ndon't do anything too risky, all right?}Tóm lại đừng làm gì nguy hiểm nhé.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.49,0:05:53.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Okay.}Ừm.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.16,0:05:59.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{And keep that with you at all times,\Nand always think of me!}Và luôn mang theo nó rồi nghĩ về tớ nhé.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.29,0:06:01.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{S-Sure.}À ừ...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.75,0:06:03.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{You absolutely have to!}Nhất định đó!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.05,0:06:06.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{And when you sleep, hold onto it\Nso that in your dreams, I can...}Và khi ngủ phải ôm vào lòng để mơ về tớ...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.30,0:06:10.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{You beast!}Đồ thú hoang!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.22,0:06:15.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Late night, after lights out in the dorm...}{\i0}Và sau khi kí túc xá tắt đèn...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.64,0:06:21.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{I'm sure the Magia Lupus are behind\Nthese events. What I think is—}Chắc chắn lũ Magia Lupus \Nđứng sau vụ này. Những gì tao nghĩ--
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.73,0:06:26.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Should we really be walking\Naround school after hours?}Đi ra khỏi phòng giờ này chẳng phải không được sao?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.94,0:06:29.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{You really are a straight arrow, aren't you.}Mày nghiêm túc nhỉ.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.07,0:06:32.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{It'll be fine if we apologize later!}Tí nữa xin lỗi sau.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.37,0:06:34.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Don't leave me alone!}Đừng bỏ tớ lại!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.24,0:06:37.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Why are you guys tagging along?}Sao bọn mày lại đi theo?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.79,0:06:44.38,Default,On-screen Text,0,0,0,,{\an8}{HEAVE-HO!}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.04,0:06:41.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Cause I want coins too, moron!}Vì tao cũng muốn có xu, thằng ngu.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.83,0:06:44.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Don't leave me all alone in that room!}Đừng bỏ tớ lại căn phòng đó.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.05,0:06:48.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{I feel bad for them.\NLet's take them with us.}Thấy bọn nó tội quá nên dẫn theo.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.05,0:06:48.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{- Huh? Are you really gonna do it?\N- I'm so scared!}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.88,0:06:51.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{I'm not sure about this.}{\i0}Càng ngày càng thấy bất ổn.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.26,0:06:56.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Hey! See that!?}Này, kia là?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.31,0:07:04.02,Default,On-screen Text,0,0,0,,{\an8}{BLOOSH}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.19,0:07:00.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{It's Lemon.}Bé Chanh.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.56,0:07:03.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{She looks so cute from behind, too.}Phía sau dễ thương quá.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.69,0:07:07.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Hey, Lemo...}Bé Chanh--
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.99,0:07:09.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Wait.}Khoan.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.28,0:07:10.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Something's wrong.}Có gì đó không đúng.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.27,0:07:41.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Hey, you've gotta be kidding me.}Này, đùa nhau à.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.69,0:07:49.57,Default,On-screen Text,0,0,0,,{\an8}{BLOOSH}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.19,0:07:45.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{She didn't have any eyes, but she was\Nso cute because it was Lemon.}Dù không có mắt nhưng vẫn dễ thương vì là bé Chanh.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.56,0:07:48.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{I just realized that.}Tao vừa nhận ra điều đó.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.94,0:07:52.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{That's definitely magic all right.}Đó chắc chắn là ma thuật.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.45,0:07:53.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{- What should we—\N- Wait.}Chúng ta phải làm gì--\N Khoan!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.45,0:07:56.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{She's going somewhere.}Cậu ấy đi đâu rồi.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.74,0:07:57.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{We gotta chase her.}Phải đuổi theo.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.91,0:08:03.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{She turned that corner.}Rẽ ngay góc đó.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.55,0:08:08.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Biến mất rồi.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.46,0:08:12.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{You're kidding, right?\NThis is a dead end.}Đùa nhau à? Đường cụt mà?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.22,0:08:16.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Hey. Did you hear something?}Nè, cậu có nghe thấy gì không?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.97,0:08:19.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Huh? I didn't hear anything.}Hả? Không.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.19,0:08:24.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{No, I do hear something.}Chắc chắn là có.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.73,0:08:26.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Like the sound of wood creaking!}Như tiếng của gỗ bị bẻ gãy.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.77,0:08:28.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Don't be spouting random bull...}Đừng có nói vớ vẩn...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.44,0:08:32.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{I heard it too. Just kill me now!}Tao cũng nghe nữa... Chết mất!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.99,0:08:33.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Lemon!}Bé Chanh!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.49,0:08:37.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Stay calm. It's just a spell.}Bình tĩnh. Ma thuật thôi.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.70,0:08:39.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Disclose.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.38,0:08:49.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{What the hell?}Cái quái gì đây?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.00,0:08:50.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{A d-door?}C-Cửa?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.47,0:08:59.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Revealing the door\Nis as far as my magic can go.}Phép của tao chỉ có thể làm hiện cánh cửa.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.18,0:09:03.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Chúng ta cần ma pháp đặc biệt để mở nó.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.06,0:09:06.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Machine Gun Explomb!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.28,0:09:13.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Damn thing won't budge!!}Mẹ nó không bị gì!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.44,0:09:15.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{What the hell are we supposed to do with it?}Phải làm sao đây?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.50,0:09:27.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{H-Hey.}N-Này...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.08,0:09:28.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Mash?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.27,0:09:54.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{He pried the door open\Nwith the power of leverage.}Nó cạy cửa bằng sức mạnh đòn bẩy...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.86,0:09:57.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Anything goes for him, huh?}Thằng này cái quái gì cũng làm được à...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.66,0:10:03.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Lemon is inside. And most likely...}Chắc chắn con Chanh trong đó.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.87,0:10:05.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{the Magia Lupus, too.}Và cả lũ Magia Lupus.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.04,0:10:13.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Don't do anything too risky, all right?}{\i0}Đừng làm gì nguy hiểm nhé?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.92,0:10:17.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{I'm sorry, but...}Xin lỗi nhưng...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.88,0:10:20.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{I don't think\NI'll be able to keep that promise.}Tớ không thể giữ lời rồi.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.68,0:10:23.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Let's go.}Đi thôi.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.10,0:10:32.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{I had no idea the school\Nhad a lower level like this.}Không ngờ trường học lại có tầng hầm.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.07,0:10:35.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{It's like a secret base. Right, Finn?}Cứ như căn cứ bí mật ấy, Finn nhỉ?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.53,0:10:37.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Y-Yeah.}À ừm.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.03,0:10:40.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{You punk! Keep killing\Nthe dramatic tension and I'll kill ya!}Thằng chó! Mày mà còn phá\N không khí căng thẳng tao giết!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.53,0:10:43.33,Default,On-screen Text,0,0,0,,{\an8}{FLUMP}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.82,0:10:42.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{I'm sorry.}Xin lỗi.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.16,0:10:44.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{I mean, I wouldn't really... Wait...}Không... ý tao không phải...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.83,0:10:46.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Look, I'm sorry too, man.}Tao cũng xin lỗi.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.29,0:10:48.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Mash, don't be so depressed.}Mash, đừng buồn.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.71,0:10:51.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{Our enemies chose this place as their hideout.}Kẻ địch hẳn phải trốn ở đây.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.29,0:10:56.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{I'm certain this location\Ngives them an advantage.}Tao nghĩ đây là sân nhà của chúng.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.88,0:11:00.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Hey, see that?}Này, nhìn kìa!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.01,0:11:01.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{There's light over there!}Có ánh sáng!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.81,0:11:10.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{An arena?}Sàn đấu?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.31,0:11:12.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{What is this?}Gì thế này?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.65,0:11:15.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Are you a little slow?}Mày bị chậm phát triển à?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.36,0:11:16.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Correct!}Chính xác.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.36,0:11:23.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{It's an ancient dueling field.}Đây là sàn đấu cổ xưa.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.37,0:11:26.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{So old that current teachers\Ndon't even know it exists.}Cổ tới nỗi chẳng thầy cô nào biết đâu.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.20,0:11:29.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Are you one of the Magia Lupus?}Mày là người của Magia Lupus?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.37,0:11:32.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Me? No, no.}Không không.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.63,0:11:35.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{I'm here at Third Fang's request.}Chỉ là tao ở đây theo yêu cầu của số 3.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.17,0:11:41.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{To eradicate intruders like you.}Để tiêu diệt lũ xâm nhập tụi mày.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.01,0:11:47.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Now, if you want to proceed,\Nyou need to wager coins and challenge me.}Muốn đi tiếp thì đặt cược và đấu với tao.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.10,0:11:49.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Though...}Mà...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.52,0:11:51.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{I'll never let you get through!}Đừng hòng thằng nào qua được.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.65,0:11:54.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Very well.}Thích thì chiều.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.40,0:11:55.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Wait.}Khoan.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.90,0:11:57.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Let me.}Để tao.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.48,0:11:58.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Dot.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.94,0:12:04.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{'Cause you know that I hate\Ngood-lookin' guys to death.}Tao ghét nhất mấy thằng đẹp mã.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.91,0:12:07.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{I see.}Thế à.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.12,0:12:08.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Go get 'im.}Cố lên.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.45,0:12:09.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Good luck.}Xử hắn nhé.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.12,0:12:14.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Hey, you know what?}Mày là loại đó nhỉ.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.17,0:12:17.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{You have a fan club, don't you?}Mày có fan club phải không?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.92,0:12:19.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{I do. What of it?}Có. Thì sao?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.09,0:12:22.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Có vẻ nó đang cay lắm.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.05,0:12:24.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Most definitely so.}Chắc chắn luôn.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.84,0:12:26.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Very likely.}Chứ gì nữa.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.89,0:12:30.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Livin' the dream, are ya!? I'll kill ya!}Thằng chó! Tao giết mày!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.56,0:12:32.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{As expected...}Biết ngay...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.77,0:12:35.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{You could say his jealousy\Nis even invigorating.}Càng cay càng mạnh.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.23,0:12:37.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{What a pitiful creature.}Thật tội nghiệp.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.65,0:12:40.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{What? You're jealous of my attractiveness?}Hả? Mày ghen tị vì tao nổi tiếng à?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.40,0:12:42.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{I am, so what!?}Thì sao?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.40,0:12:42.07,Default,On-screen Text,0,0,0,,{\an8}{RAH}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.57,0:12:44.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{You can be jealous and all that.}Thích thì cứ ghen tị.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.11,0:12:50.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Well, since you lack both a good face\Nand good brains, I don't see how I could lose.}Cơ mà mày vừa ngu vừa xấu \Nnên chẳng thể nào tao thua đâu.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.20,0:12:52.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Rose Whip.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.38,0:13:01.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Though they came here to rescue Lemon,}{\i0}Họ đến để cứu bé Chanh.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.01,0:13:08.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{the ugly battle of Dot Barrett, envious\Nof a handsome boy, was about to begin.}{\i0}Nhưng thằng xấu trai Dot Barrett do\N ghen tị với trai đẹp nên lao vào đánh nhau.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.47,0:13:15.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{This is the Bureau of Magic,\Nthe Magic Realm's highest legal authority.}{\i0}Đây là cục Ma thuật. \NCơ quan quyền lực nhất cõi Ma thuật.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.77,0:13:20.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Mr. Wahlberg.\NI apologize for the sudden call.}Xin lỗi vì gọi ngài đến gấp, ngài Wahlberg.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.23,0:13:22.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{No need for apologies.}Không cần xin lỗi.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.69,0:13:26.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{But the fact that you called for me means...}Nhưng cho gọi ta tức là...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.78,0:13:27.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{That's right.}Vâng.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.32,0:13:33.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Six of death row's most notorious inmates\Nhave escaped from Hecatrice.}Sáu tử tù khét tiếng nhất đã trốn thoát khỏi Hecatrice.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.87,0:13:37.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{The prison guards were slaughtered.}Các cai ngục đã bị giết sạch.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.17,0:13:39.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{And they were assisted by...}Và chúng được hỗ trợ bởi...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.38,0:13:43.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Innocent Zero.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.68,0:13:51.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Meanwhile, in the underground arena,\NDot was jealous of the handsome guy.}{\i0}Trong khi đó, ở dưới lòng đất, \NDot ghen tị với thằng đẹp mã.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.89,0:13:52.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Eat this!}Nhận lấy!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.06,0:13:54.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Explomb!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.24,0:14:07.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{You guys beat Silva\Nthe second-year, didn't you?}Bọn này đã đánh bại anh Silva năm 2 nhỉ?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.08,0:14:14.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{A-Actually he maybe kinda\Nbeat the crap outta me.}T-Thực ra tao bị nó đánh bầm dập...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.16,0:14:19.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{It's a shame a guy like him\Nis a double-liner.}Anh ta có tận 2 vạch... phí phạm thật.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.29,0:14:24.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{But magic capacity is worthless\Nif you don't use it right.}Năng lực là vô dụng nếu không biết cách dùng.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.05,0:14:27.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{I'll say this outright.}Để tao nói trước.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.59,0:14:30.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{I'm a lot tougher than he is.}Tao mạnh hơn anh ta lắm đấy.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.47,0:14:32.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Oh?}Thế à?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.31,0:14:36.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Well, I'm definitely not gonna lose.}Vậy thì tao sẽ không thua.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.56,0:14:39.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{How do you intend on winning?}Sao mày chắc thắng thế?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.65,0:14:41.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Like this!}Vì thế này đây!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.90,0:14:43.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Explombomb!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.24,0:14:53.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{What are these?}{\i0}Chúng là gì?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.20,0:14:55.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Marks on the ground?}Dấu trên sàn?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.08,0:14:58.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Hey, might wanna watch your step!}Đừng có di chuyển lung tung.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.04,0:15:01.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{This is a conditional spell.}Câu chú điều kiện đấy.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.42,0:15:04.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{It's got five times\Nthe explosive power than usual!}Sức công phá gấp 5 bình thường.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.13,0:15:08.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{There's no way I would fall\Nfor such an obvious trap.}Nghĩ sao tao lại dính vô cái bẫy rõ ràng này?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.76,0:15:09.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Not me.}Không bao giờ.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.80,0:15:11.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Nah.}Không.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.34,0:15:16.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{A guy like you is sure to fall for it!}Mày chắc chắn sẽ dính bẫy.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.64,0:15:23.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{How does he intend on making me\Nstep on these marks?}{\i0}Hắn làm sao để bắt mình dẫm vào nó?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.27,0:15:27.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Is there a way to move me from this spot?}{\i0}Hay nó có thể di chuyển?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.53,0:15:30.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{I won't fall for that trick.}Tao không bị dụ đâu nhé.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.07,0:15:33.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Rose Whip Absol.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.49,0:15:38.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Machine Gun Explomb!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.79,0:15:41.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Damn it, it's not working!}Mẹ nó, không ảnh hưởng!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.79,0:15:43.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Grab.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.76,0:15:48.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{My wand!}Gậy phép của tao!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.17,0:15:51.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Stab.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.84,0:15:55.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{That hurts!}Đau quá!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.72,0:16:00.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Those thorns have completely\Nimmobilized your body.}Những cái gai sẽ khiến mày bất động đấy.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.52,0:16:04.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{That tacky bandanna with those goofy eyes?}Cái khăn trùm đầu dơ bẩn và cặp mắt chó chết.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.56,0:16:07.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{And lacking sense in magic to boot.}Và không có cảm thụ ma thuật.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.44,0:16:12.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{You ultimately failed in making me\Nstep on these marks, too.}Kết cục không thể làm tao giẫm lên dấu ma pháp.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.61,0:16:16.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{You really are a far cry from handsome.}Mày đúng là kém cỏi.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.45,0:16:20.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{My next attack will definitely finish you off.}Đòn tiếp theo sẽ kết thúc.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.66,0:16:22.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Stop it!}Dừng lại!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.79,0:16:23.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Drop.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.04,0:16:30.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{I never said anything about\Nmaking you step on the marks.}Tao chưa từng nói sẽ dụ mày giẫm lên nó.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.89,0:16:41.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Explombomb is nothing more\Nthan a time bomb.}Explombomb là bom hẹn giờ.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.69,0:16:49.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Didn't think I'd confidently set time bombs\Nright in front of your face, did ya?}Không nghĩ rằng tao dám đặt bom \Nhẹn giờ ngay trước mặt mày hả?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.82,0:16:54.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{I'll kill ya eightfold!}Chết với tao thằng nhãi!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.78,0:16:59.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{H-How can I, to someone like him...}{\i0}S-Sao có thể... một tên như thế...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.50,0:17:10.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Don't judge everything\Nby their looks, pretty boy!}Đừng phán xét bất cứ thứ gì qua vẻ ngoài.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.17,0:17:12.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{You did it, Dot!}Tuyệt quá, Dot!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.13,0:17:15.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{There's no way I'd lose!}Nghĩ sao tao thua được.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.80,0:17:18.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Yeah! Bring on the next guy!}Gọi hết bọn nó ra đây!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.11,0:17:31.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{This punk. Striking an attractive pose,\Neven in defeat...}{\i0}Thằng chó. Bị đánh bại còn ra vẻ!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.40,0:17:34.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{He sure is unwavering.}{\i0}Nó thật kiên định.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.36,0:17:37.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{I don't exactly hate that.}{\i0}Tao không ghét điều đó.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.28,0:17:39.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Is it over?}Xong rồi à?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.04,0:17:42.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Wh-What the hell!?}C-Cái quái gì?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.41,0:17:45.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{I'm getting sucked into the ground.}Mình bị kẹt trên mặt đất.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.54,0:17:48.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Please, save my baby.\NAt least spare this one.}Hãy cứu thằng bé. Ít nhất hãy cứu nó.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.08,0:17:52.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{I assume this means our enemies\Nhave no intention of letting us g...}Có vẻ kẻ thù không định để chúng ta...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.71,0:17:56.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{I'm sinking! I'm going to sink!}Tớ đang chìm! Đang chìm nè!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.51,0:17:59.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{I think these guys...}{\i0}Bọn này...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.60,0:18:02.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{are even more insane than I am?}{\i0}...ngu hơn mình luôn thì phải...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.66,0:18:21.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Their plan is to split us up\Nand hunt us down.}Kế hoạch là phân tách cả nhóm ra à.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.91,0:18:27.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{The double-liner first-year...}Năm nhất 2 vạch...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.96,0:18:34.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{I was more interested\Nin seeing Mushroom Head.}Mình thích chơi với đầu nấm hơn.
